description:
About the Talk:
Let's talk about career management. In this meetup, we will talk about three critical elements of career management, each of which could have a direct impact on a job search. We will go into personal branding, networking (and "networking on steroids"), and developing multiple revenue streams. Come with questions and challenges you are facing to have a lively discussion.

About the Speaker:
Jason Alba started his IT career as a web developer and has since had various responsibilities, from email administrator to network admin to tech support to various developer roles. He conceptualized and owns JibberJobber.com, a CRM for job seekers. Recently he has focused on marketing and product management for Saas products. Jason is a Pluralsight author with 34 courses focusing on careers, soft skills, and professional development. He is active on Twitter: @jasonalba
title: Virtual Meetup - Career Management with Jason Alba
